  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "FCA specific focus area of livelihoods is small-scale entrepreneurship with emphasis on women and youths. FCA supports technical education and vocational training to the out of school youths and rural women striving to ensure their livelihood either through employment or post training entrepreneurship. Promotion of enterprise and employment aims to diversify and create off- and non-farm livelihood options for those who have no or limited access to land or are otherwise unable to farm, and thus depend on earned income for food and subsistence."
    },
